      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOOKED ON METAL (3) pinged the lids and led for most of the way to hold a minor placing when second and beaten a nose (20.06) at this track in a Maiden over 352m. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Rates highly and will give a great sight. ANOTHER ZULU (1) made a big impression on debut when started big odds last time but hit the ground running with a strong early split, giving a sight but fading only late to finish second (20.32) at this track over 352m. Improver who must come into calculations on debut effort. MIGHTY GENIE (2) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only 2.5 lengths (22.69) at this track. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Worth following up. ANOTHER BOWL CUT (8) is by Aussie Infrared out of Manipulate making debut. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Can sneak into the frame at her first appearance.",
